      "cmd": {
        "21": "00"
      },
      "freq": 3,
      "description": "K-Line KWP2000 only (ISO 14230-4 fast init). ECU address 0x11, tester 0xF1. Init sequence: ATTP5, ATSH 81 11 F1. Confirmed on Suzuki Cultus 2016 Pakistan (Alto K10 / K10B engine) and expected to apply to Suzuki Swift 1999 which shares the same Engine ECU platform. Response header: 61 00, followed by 65 data bytes. All bix offsets are into the data bytes only (i.e. after stripping the 2-byte 61 00 response header). Byte map was reverse-engineered from the SZ Viewer Android APK (Engine_KWP_00_Local$ class) and confirmed by live driving correlation.",
